:46+00:00\" class=\"wp-block-latest-posts__post-date\">July 2, 2020</time></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://wordpressa.local/wordpressa/archives/323\">Block: Image</a><time datetime=\"2020-07-02T09:28:46+00:00\" class=\"wp-block-latest-posts__post-date\">July 2, 2020</time></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://wordpressa.local/wordpressa/archives/322\">Block: Gallery</a><time datetime=\"2020-07-02T09:28:46+00:00\" class=\"wp-block-latest-posts__post-date\">July 2, 2020</time></li>\n</ul>\n\n\n<p>Grid view, now sorted from A -Z.</p>\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-latest-posts wp-block-latest-posts__list is-grid columns-3\"><li><a href=\"http://wordpressa.local/wordpressa/archives/301\">(no title)</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://wordpressa.local/wordpressa/archives/238\">(no title)</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://wordpressa.local/wordpressa/archives/237\">(no title)</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://wordpressa.local/wordpressa/archives/236\">(no title)</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://wordpressa.local/wordpressa/archives/263\">2014-slider-mobile-behavior</a></li>\n</ul>\n\n\n<p>You can also change the number of columns used to display the latest posts. The block below only displays posts from the Block category:</p>\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-latest-posts wp-block-latest-posts__list is-grid columns-5 has-dates\"></ul>\n\n\n<p>Search widget:</p>\n\n\n<form class=\"wp-block-search\" role=\"search\" method=\"get\" action=\"http://wordpressa.local/wordpressa/\"><label for=\"wp-block-search__input-1\" class=\"wp-block-search__label\">Search</label><input type=\"search\" id=\"wp-block-search__input-1\" class=\"wp-block-search__input\" name=\"s\" value=\"\" placeholder=\"\" required /><button type=\"submit\" class=\"wp-block-search__button\">Search</button></form>\n\n\n<p>Tag Cloud widget:</p>\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-tag-cloud\">Your site doesn&#8217;t have any tags, so there&#8217;s nothing to display here at the moment.</p>\n\n\n<p>RSS Feed widget:</p>\n\n\n<div class=\"components-placeholder\"><div 